# create IAM role & attach it to EC2 instance.
# minimize access -- minimum IAM policies , search for IAM -- roles ---create role
# this role going to attach to EC2 so select EC2 we need to add privileges like EC2 full access , cloudformation, IAM 
# however to avoid permission related issues we will use AdministrationAccess (not recommended)

# rolename   --- eksctl-role
need to add it to our EC2 instance.
steps:
EC2- Actions - security- modify IAM - eksctl-role
